what black power really means!

892
00:56:14,490 --> 00:56:17,730
And furthermore to that,
you ain't all that good-lookin'!

893
00:56:25,730 --> 00:56:27,490
That was very good.

894
00:56:27,570 --> 00:56:31,090
If I come in again, remind me about
the Oregon Boysenberry, will you?

895
00:56:32,210 --> 00:56:34,170
Yeah, I sure will.
Thank you, sir.

896
00:56:37,610 --> 00:56:39,810
Should we take home
a couple of quarts for dessert?

897
00:56:39,890 --> 00:56:41,730
No, Tillie's baked some pies.

898
00:56:52,410 --> 00:56:54,290
You stupid idiot!

899
00:56:57,130 --> 00:56:59,050
Why can't you
look where you're going?

900
00:56:59,130 --> 00:57:01,290
Sorry, son,
but your car is so low...

901
00:57:01,370 --> 00:57:03,330
Of course you didn't see me!

902
00:57:03,410 --> 00:57:05,410
You weren't even looking
where you were going!

903
00:57:05,490 --> 00:57:07,730
Look what you did to my car!

904
00:57:07,810 --> 00:57:09,450
It's my fault.
My insurance...

905
00:57:09,490 --> 00:57:12,130
Yeah, yeah. Who cares
about your lousy insurance?

906
00:57:12,170 --> 00:57:14,090
I worked over three months on that!

907
00:57:14,130 --> 00:57:16,090
