to have it repaired?

908
00:57:16,170 --> 00:57:19,530
Look at it! Thirty or forty bucks
it'll cost. Did you see it?

909
00:57:19,610 --> 00:57:21,690
Stupid old man.
He oughtn't be allowed out.

910
00:57:21,770 --> 00:57:24,090
He ought to be put away someplace
in a home or something.

911
00:57:24,130 --> 00:57:27,770
There's fifty bucks! Don't bother
to have it fixed. Buy a new one!

912
00:57:29,570 --> 00:57:31,610
Some of these old guys,
they're senile!

913
00:57:32,650 --> 00:57:34,370
Stupid old man.

914
00:57:35,170 --> 00:57:37,010
There oughta be a law!

