00:58:37,450 --> 00:58:40,250
I can't tell you
how happy I am for you.

933
00:58:40,330 --> 00:58:43,010
And the whole thing having
happened so quickly.

934
00:58:43,050 --> 00:58:45,130
You remember what it was
with Peter and me.

935
00:58:45,210 --> 00:58:47,090
It took us three years
to decide to get married...

936
00:58:47,130 --> 00:58:48,810
and we'd been living together
for two.

937
00:58:52,890 --> 00:58:54,170
To John and Joey.

938
00:58:54,250 --> 00:58:57,090
John and Joanna. He won't call me
anything but Joanna.

939
00:58:57,170 --> 00:58:59,330
- I'm beginning to like it too.
- To John and Joanna.

940
00:59:02,250 --> 00:59:05,570
